      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Mesh convergence study performed on the pedicle screw-rod construct; peak von Mises stress and construct stiffness showed less than 2% change between medium and fine mesh densities. Gradation 2 achieved."
    },
