      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Linear elastic continuum model with frictional contact at screw-rod interface. Model form is well-established for metallic implant stiffness prediction under quasi-static loading and is consistent with prior published validation studies."
