      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Testing performed under a single load condition per ASTM F1717 compression-bending protocol. Variation in test conditions (e.g., multiple load levels, off-axis loading) was not explored, limiting achieved level to gradation 2, below the required gradation 3."
